So if you think back on that moment when
you walk into your boss's office and say,

114
00:06:04.890 --> 00:06:08.390
that's it, I'm done,
what leads up to that.

115
00:06:08.390 --> 00:06:09.480
So most commonly

116
00:06:10.610 --> 00:06:14.070
It's gonna be that you have another
job alternative that you prefer.

117
00:06:14.070 --> 00:06:17.700
And so you've compared your
current job to an alternative and

118
00:06:17.700 --> 00:06:19.990
you've decided I'm gonna leave.

119
00:06:19.990 --> 00:06:20.900
How would you've got there?

120
00:06:22.420 --> 00:06:26.460
Well sometimes somebody might of
called you and just offer you a job.

