00:06:37.590 --> 00:06:40.360
So somewhere along the line you
decided to search for a job.

126
00:06:41.540 --> 00:06:43.590
Why did you decide to search for a job?

127
00:06:43.590 --> 00:06:45.220
Again, there could be multiple reasons for
that.

128
00:06:45.220 --> 00:06:49.340
So the most common is probably
that you don't like your job, but

129
00:06:49.340 --> 00:06:53.110
it might also be that you've heard
that all of your friends are going and

130
00:06:53.110 --> 00:06:56.270
getting great pay raises and
great jobs In new firms and

131
00:06:56.270 --> 00:06:59.350
you think, maybe that means I
should look around as well.

132
00:07:00.630 --> 00:07:04.280
There are other paths as well so
some people may have said

