00:07:04.280 --> 00:07:07.540
after three year I going to graduate
school, and so that's not going

134
00:07:07.540 --> 00:07:10.660
to have very much to do with how they
feel about their job or the alternatives.

135
00:07:10.660 --> 00:07:13.390
Of course some people might
just walk into the office and

136
00:07:13.390 --> 00:07:16.740
say, I quit without even having
thought About an alternative job.

137
00:07:17.740 --> 00:07:20.970
Basic point here, so lots of different
ways this decision is made and

138
00:07:20.970 --> 00:07:22.590
different considerations in each of them.

139
00:07:22.590 --> 00:07:24.969
And so
maybe we shouldn't be that surprised,

140
00:07:24.969 --> 00:07:28.690
that the satisfaction with our job and
the satisfaction with our manager

