So we may have some ideas about
what we want to do with our lives.

157
00:08:27.840 --> 00:08:31.120
I can say for a start,
I never expected to be an academic.

158
00:08:31.120 --> 00:08:33.960
I always thought I was gonna be a manager,
consultant,

