00:09:31.300 --> 00:09:32.400
So early on in our career,

179
00:09:32.400 --> 00:09:34.970
we don't really have a good idea of
what we like, what we're good at.

180
00:09:34.970 --> 00:09:37.620
We'll hop around jobs a bit
while we figure it out.

181
00:09:37.620 --> 00:09:39.100
Later on we've got more information.

